{"TopicId":170456,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Stock guns","CreatedByName":"EXTREME_GAMER_4","CreatedById":184988,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-03T23:30:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EXTREME_GAMER_4","CreatedById":184988,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-03T23:30:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Georgia, serif;\u0022\u003EI\u2019ve tried and failed again, and again at making stock weapons and I was wondering if one of my fellow KSP players could help or recommend ideas.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-07T04:20:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe structural fuselage makes a line barrel. Pit a rhino on max thrust behind it and make a projectile, Punch the rhino, and let it fly!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-08T03:02:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/NfYVhLVcf3I?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EXTREME_GAMER_4","CreatedById":184988,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-08T22:01:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223288188\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221517977257\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheMadKraken2297\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/6/2018 at 11:20 PM, TheMadKraken2297 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe structural fuselage makes a line barrel. Pit a rhino on max thrust behind it and make a projectile, Punch the rhino, and let it fly!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, that would make a great canon, but I was thinking more along the lines of machine guns on airplanes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EXTREME_GAMER_4","CreatedById":184988,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-08T23:40:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223289149\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518058944\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151713\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fourfa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, fourfa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/NfYVhLVcf3I?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, but like I told someone else, I was thinking more along the lines of guns on planes.But I will try this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T00:17:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, ok then! For that I use the radial decoupler attached to sepeartrons. Separatrons make awesome ammo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fearless Son","CreatedById":133397,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T01:04:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223289911\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518135429\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheMadKraken2297\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n39 minutes ago, TheMadKraken2297 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, ok then! For that I use the radial decoupler attached to sepeartrons. Separatrons make awesome ammo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeperatrons on radial decouplers are more like launchable rockets (specifically two seperatrons mirrored on either side of a radial decoupler) that you can stack on top of one another to make things like air-to-surface rocket pods on ground-attack craft. \u00A0Not really possible to make a friable machine gun in stock, but you can make things that look like they could be a machine gun in stock. \u00A0I have seen the M-Beam 200 I-Beam Pocket Edition used as a frame for weapons, with things like the\u00A0Communotron 16 as a barrel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T01:09:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo you want fake machineguns? Because if you want to make actual stock, belt-fed 50 cals or something, that is impossible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T01:50:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is going to end up being craft sharing, and so the thread has been moved to the craft sharing subforum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EXTREME_GAMER_4","CreatedById":184988,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T03:40:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223289980\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518138558\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo you want fake machineguns? Because if you want to make \u003Cu\u003Eactual stock, belt-fed 50 cals or something, that is impossible.\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m not an actual newbie but IT IS?!?!?!?!?!?\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T04:13:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas that supposed to be sarcastic? Obviously it is. There are mods that give you the possibility of using weapons:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3693583698\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155014-13x-bdarmory-continued-v1000-1142017-vessel-mover-camera-tools-bdmk22-destruction-effects-burn-together/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook at the parts in your unmodded save. Do you see any belts? Firing mechanisms? Parts that are \u003Cem\u003Etwelve \u003Cstrong\u003Emillimeters\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E in diameter? Is your Communotron 16 bored through like a barrel? No, it\u0027s a perfectly average antenna. You can\u0027t make actual guns in unmodded KSP, so you have to stick with rocket propelled projectiles, or go the modding way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Servo","CreatedById":149419,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T04:16:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223289980\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518138558\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo you want fake machineguns? Because if you want to make actual stock, belt-fed 50 cals or something, that is impossible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t say that too loudly, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002238787\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@klond\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0might hear you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022eIMbGci.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/eIMbGci.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it is possible to create a number of machine-gun like turrets. Most rely on dropping small parts (this one uses thermometers, but some use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls instead) in front of a jet/rocket engine. However, it isn\u0027t practical to use a belt-feed system. Instead, they are typically hopper-fed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a particularly good example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/klond/rapidfire-cannon\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/klond/rapidfire-cannon\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eagle92lightning","CreatedById":170551,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-09T21:54:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223290012\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518141014\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is going to end up being craft sharing, and so the thread has been moved to the craft sharing subforum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo true, Any ways I have tried my hand at railguns that could possibly fire pretty large pieces of ammo (1.25m stack decoupers) and you could even apply a spin by rolling while firing (make sure the gun is centered for this)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-11T09:48:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStock shotgun, max spread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1131290958\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://gfycat.com/HealthyCapitalChickadee\u0022 style=\u0022height:673px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurious ... some gifs do load, others fail.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick the link to see the shotgun with minimal spread.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://gfycat.com/IgnorantAridBlobfish\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://gfycat.com/IgnorantAridBlobfish\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"selfish_meme","CreatedById":125899,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-12T08:45:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@swdennis\u00A0 has built a cartridge fed gun, but it was a bit to big to be mounted on a plane, not sure if stock, pretty sure he used tweakscale\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZE2Fsnuz6xo?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}